@startuml UC16_Dashboard
title UC-16: Xem Dashboard tổng quan (CEO / HR / Admin)

actor "CEO / HR / Admin" as User
participant "Web Dashboard" as Web
participant "API Server" as API
database "Database" as DB

User -> Web : Đăng nhập thành công\n→ Trang Dashboard hiển thị

Web -> API : GET /dashboard/summary
API -> DB : -- KPI ngày hôm nay --\nSELECT COUNT(*) total_employees FROM Employee\nWHERE status='active'
API -> DB : SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT employee_id)\nFROM AttendanceRecord\nWHERE type='check_in' AND DATE(timestamp)=TODAY
API -> DB : SELECT COUNT(*) checked_in_count,\nSUM(CASE WHEN is_late THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) late_count\nFROM AttendanceRecord\nWHERE DATE(timestamp)=TODAY
API -> DB : SELECT COUNT(*) fraud_alerts\nFROM FraudDetection fd\nJOIN AttendanceRecord ar ON fd.record_id=ar.record_id\nWHERE DATE(ar.timestamp)=TODAY\nAND (mock_location_detected OR gps_spoofing_detected\nOR buddy_punch_suspected)
DB --> API : Aggregated KPIs

API -> DB : SELECT lat, lng, altitude, employee_id\nFROM AttendanceRecord\nWHERE type='check_in' AND status='approved'\nAND DATE(timestamp)=TODAY\nAND (chưa check_out)
DB --> API : Active employee locations

API --> Web : {\n  total_employees,\n  checked_in_today,\n  on_time_rate (%),\n  fraud_alerts_today,\n  active_locations: [...]\n}

Web --> User : Hiển thị Dashboard:\n- KPI cards\n- Mini bản đồ vị trí nhân viên\n- Biểu đồ tỷ lệ đúng giờ

== Auto refresh ==
loop Mỗi 60 giây
    Web -> API : GET /dashboard/summary
    API --> Web : Updated data
    Web --> User : Cập nhật Dashboard
end

@enduml
